How to play:

Each round is split between a 'morning' and a 'night' phase.

The game starts in the 'morning', where all users vote to eliminate who they believe the werewolf is. If the werewolf survives the 'morning', the 'night' phase follows. In this phase, the werewolf may anonymously eliminate any other player we wishes.

There will also be one healer who may anonymously choose to protect ONE user including him/herself, per round, from death in the following night phase.

This game will only end if all other users except the werewolf is eliminated, or if the werewolf gets eliminated.

How to win:

You are the werewolf, hiding in plain sight as a regular human. Your goal is to Eliminate all other users without getting caught.

 

 

Sign in or create an account to get started!
